author: Top Gear
description:
We’re taking a look forward at all the incredible cars coming this year including everything from 2000hp hypercars to 1000hp hypercars, plus $20,000 pick-up trucks, brands being brought back from the dead, brands you’ve never heard of, a whole host of restomods, and even a hot hatch. 2026 is lining up to be quite a year!
